üî• CCEE POWER MEMORY (VERY IMPORTANT)
SOX ‚Üí Financial reporting controls (mandatory ‚Äì US)
SOC ‚Üí Assurance reports for service organizations
COBIT ‚Üí Governance & control
ITIL ‚Üí Service management & operations
Golden Rule for Exam:
Governance = COBIT | Services = ITIL | Assurance = SOC | Law = SOX
